Title: A Nebb in Need
Description:
You! You no spider. Please, must help before spiders come again. 

Nebb know Chittering Den. Never seen spiders here before. Eat grubs, eat kobolds. But spiders dark things from dark places. Hate light.

Can't leave post. You take candles, yes? Light up barricade. Keep spiders away.
ObjectivesText: Collect the Bundle of Candles and place candles along the barricade.
CompletionText: Keep away dark. Keep away spiders.
